  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Note
  noteText: The collector, consumed by the paintings, dismisses others' concerns
    as madness, believing only he comprehends their visual "truth." He plans to hide
    the final piece, convinced the paintings speak to him, and searches for a key,
    frustrated by others' attempts to destroy them.
